32:51.807 --> 33:00.552
they're not always amenable to that kind of 
advice, to put it mildly, and you can't do anything

32:51.807 --> 33:00.552
about that. But I believe if you're honest up 
front, you're okay. Do you think planetary

33:05.611 --> 33:09.999
astronomy is kind of mined out as regards big 
